		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SPAIN_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>*A miracle has occured! A young student appears to have risen from the dead*[NEWLINE]I pray constantly for supplication, this must be a sign! God's gift to us all. Bring the holy vessel to me!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SPAIN_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*Our enemies brazenly disregard our beliefs and bring dishonour onto God*[NEWLINE]If we are to prevail it is because God wills it. Every retinue of Knights should contain not just squires and retainers, but priests as well: to show that we fight for God.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SPAIN_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*The priests of the Grand Temple submit a request for huge amounts of gold and manpower for their architectural vision*[NEWLINE]How inspired are the men of God! They shall have all they require, and more!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SPAIN_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*The Age of Discovery is upon us, and the deeds of our Conquistadors have captured the imagination of the nation*[NEWLINE]Just and righteous are the warriors of the Crown. Let it be known that any who bring back the treasures of the New World will be rewarded, in this life and in the next.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SPAIN_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>*Our settlements and conquests have led to large scale discontent amongst the assimilated peoples, opinion is worsening*[NEWLINE]We cannot bring back the gods and kings they have lost, but we can let them find a new way of life, in harmony with ours, and with love and hope for all.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SPAIN_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>*The fixtures of our great imperial history are as grand as they are important, it is for this reason that the peoples of the world wish to visit Spain*[NEWLINE]We cannot stop the tides of this brave new world any longer. The history of Spain is the history of the world. Let all come and see.</Text>
